# distributions.
#
# If you have any problems with Mendeley's Debian/Ubuntu repositories,
# you can let us know at http://feedback.mendeley.com

# CSG have configured this file to be overwritten automatically.
# This is to prevent update requests being displayed to non-admin users.
# If you have a Kerberos root principal on your own machine and you want
# Mendeley to dial home:
# (i) ksu to root
# (ii) touch /etc/apt/sources.list.d/mendeleydesktop.list-special
# (iii) edit this file and uncomment the line below.

